verse.lines:
{lang-eng}Jesus, may all confess Thy name,
Thy wondrous love adore;
And, seeking thee, themselves inflame
To seek thee more and more.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Thee, Jesus, May Our Voices Bless,
Thee May We Love Alone;
And Ever In Our Lives Express
The Image Of Thine Own.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}O Jesus! thou the beauty art
Of angel worlds above;
Thy name is music to the heart
Inflaming it with love.{/lang-eng}
